{"tid":2259363,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我唔讚成捐錢俾612，唔夠資源嘅情況之下咁樣無疑係承認失敗，輸少當贏。","createTime":"2020-10-26T18:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T09:54:57.000Z","uid":158270,"like":17,"dislike":111,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"3e5db352c2280a8b9930bea82b17718877b9641b","tid":2259363,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T18:36:03.000Z","msg":"贏唔係坐少幾年監，而係推翻政權。<br />\n<br />\n而推翻政權需要武力，而武力來源就係武器、人力、組織、技術同渠道。所以資源應該擺喺呢啲地方。律師費、堂費無助勝利，但就可以緩和痛苦。但痛苦過後，香港仍然沉淪。以長遠計，都係死路一條。<br />\n<br />\n短期嘅誘因龐大，我亦贊成資源要用以挽救人才。但論效率，律師費同堂費都一大舊。咁我寧願直接俾手足或其家人。<br />\n長期而言，資源應投放喺上面五項，就算依家冇機會，都儲起等機會嚟。<br />\n<br />\n有人話我對手足無情冷血，我只可以話對唔住，我真係冇咁多錢幫你請律師，而且仲會有淨去打呢場仗。"},{"pid":"6eec7182b5d8fb298555da97d4342a034cc01b3f","tid":2259363,"uid":8014,"like":15,"dislike":10,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T18:54:16.000Z","msg":"夜喇 早抖發夢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連唔洗流血嘅大罷工都做唔到<br />\n<br />\n幻想要人送命嘅武力推翻政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f7af8a171ca8479e02a068fb1b9d87185f30bf","tid":2259363,"uid":33874,"like":7,"dislike":10,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T18:55:37.000Z","msg":"佢地最需要嘅係我地嘅thoughts and prayers 🙏"},{"pid":"2a7c387adafbceaf31b88e175a8b5383fe51cfcd","tid":2259363,"uid":158270,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6eec7182b5d8fb298555da97d4342a034cc01b3f","tid":2259363,"uid":8014,"like":15,"dislike":10,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T18:54:16.000Z","msg":"夜喇 早抖發夢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連唔洗流血嘅大罷工都做唔到<br />\n<br />\n幻想要人送命嘅武力推翻政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T18:57:02.000Z","msg":"兩件事唔同，全民罷工分分鐘難過武力革命。<br />\n所以先有人講笑話香港人打仗都要返工。"},{"pid":"69af381f080c76146ccd0a73a24779d6395793d0","tid":2259363,"uid":158270,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a1f7af8a171ca8479e02a068fb1b9d87185f30bf","tid":2259363,"uid":33874,"like":7,"dislike":10,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T18:55:37.000Z","msg":"佢地最需要嘅係我地嘅thoughts and prayers 🙏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T18:57:57.000Z","msg":"我都希望佢哋平安"},{"pid":"ae04ed6b8e6ab4f7e4bf448628979b0329c005ba","tid":2259363,"uid":56550,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T18:57:57.000Z","msg":"俾錢救一班唔會再出到黎抗爭既人<br />\n都唔買戰略物資<br />\n屌你買枝石屎鑽都有用過拎黎請律師啦"},{"pid":"03bfa27cf98e7cdb85cfbb54b305c64b08a2ddcf","tid":2259363,"uid":33874,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ae04ed6b8e6ab4f7e4bf448628979b0329c005ba","tid":2259363,"uid":56550,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T18:57:57.000Z","msg":"俾錢救一班唔會再出到黎抗爭既人<br />\n都唔買戰略物資<br />\n屌你買枝石屎鑽都有用過拎黎請律師啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T19:00:41.000Z","msg":"請律師為手足打係天經地義<br />\n但人地而家三權合作"},{"pid":"7a610df35e76824096bf6d38427d9415f0720ea5","tid":2259363,"uid":158270,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ae04ed6b8e6ab4f7e4bf448628979b0329c005ba","tid":2259363,"uid":56550,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T18:57:57.000Z","msg":"俾錢救一班唔會再出到黎抗爭既人<br />\n都唔買戰略物資<br />\n屌你買枝石屎鑽都有用過拎黎請律師啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T19:00:51.000Z","msg":"想買嘅人唔想冒險，冒險嘅人難搵到人出錢，佢哋之間缺嘅係渠道同組織。<br />\n所以就有人諗不如捐錢幫手足打官司，雖然效果完全唔同，但都叫心安理得。<br />\n但心安理得唔代表有效，唔代表對勝利有幫助。"},{"pid":"f036b5fdc9c9bffcb02ab9c2c219b0fa12c0c704","tid":2259363,"uid":54623,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ae04ed6b8e6ab4f7e4bf448628979b0329c005ba","tid":2259363,"uid":56550,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime