like":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1be2766459fbc383f8100efd8c4d4f19f4c54ea7","tid":2259363,"uid":158270,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebf4347de40bc5c9670d8f82de60f56550f496ee","tid":2259363,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T19:30:29.000Z","msg":"你收撚皮啦建軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講埋啲垃圾借口"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T19:36:57.000Z","msg":"你小心已墮入失敗主義圈套。建軍唔係垃圾借口。老實講，我估唔到你把口咁臭。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T19:37:57.000Z","msg":"哩個係現實<br />\n唔撚通我同你講十層樓跳落嚟會唔死又係失敗主義咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T19:47:24.000Z","msg":"建軍係垃圾借口係現實？<br />\n呢個咪失敗主義囉，建軍打仗嘅成功率更高，你唔可以因為目光短淺而嘲諷宏大目標。<br />\n我明你已經放棄光復香港嘅目標，不過咁唔代表我都要同你一樣放棄，然後再歸咎所謂現實，然後嘲笑其他人話佢哋理想主義。你想捐錢以求心安理得，與我無關。我亦冇興趣學你。"},{"pid":"1ad4ceb6ae05308a92bac8c3adab4af076bbb378","tid":2259363,"uid":245849,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3e5db352c2280a8b9930bea82b17718877b9641b","tid":2259363,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T18:36:03.000Z","msg":"贏唔係坐少幾年監，而係推翻政權。<br />\n<br />\n而推翻政權需要武力，而武力來源就係武器、人力、組織、技術同渠道。所以資源應該擺喺呢啲地方。律師費、堂費無助勝利，但就可以緩和痛苦。但痛苦過後，香港仍然沉淪。以長遠計，都係死路一條。<br />\n<br />\n短期嘅誘因龐大，我亦贊成資源要用以挽救人才。但論效率，律師費同堂費都一大舊。咁我寧願直接俾手足或其家人。<br />\n長期而言，資源應投放喺上面五項，就算依家冇機會，都儲起等機會嚟。<br />\n<br />\n有人話我對手足無情冷血，我只可以話對唔住，我真係冇咁多錢幫你請律師，而且仲會有淨去打呢場仗。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T19:57:14.000Z","msg":"家陣唔捐啲錢都唔會走咗去買槍，事實買槍亦唔需要咁多錢；你唔捐，啲錢都會其他方面去咗，所以就算我不斷屌律師費用高同條數唔透明，我都支持大家捐。做得差好過冇做，最少６１２存在本身冇錯。"},{"pid":"2b56b8688839f73df4ff65a020c5c991275062e7","tid":2259363,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a3bce4dce43e84ff3662747ab3df1d78cff91fd0","tid":2259363,"uid":216776,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2a7c387adafbceaf31b88e175a8b5383fe51cfcd","tid":2259363,"uid":158270,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6eec7182b5d8fb298555da97d4342a034cc01b3f","tid":2259363,"uid":8014,"like":15,"dislike":10,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T18:54:16.000Z","msg":"夜喇 早抖發夢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連唔洗流血嘅大罷工都做唔到<br />\n<br />\n幻想要人送命嘅武力推翻政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T18:57:02.000Z","msg":"兩件事唔同，全民罷工分分鐘難過武力革命。<br />\n所以先有人講笑話香港人打仗都要返工。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T19:02:17.000Z","msg":"推翻咩政權？港共定支共？個分別好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T19:59:29.000Z","msg":"支共無敵！不可戰勝！戰無不勝！不戰而勝！"},{"pid":"d591a4d8d8fd35322997a9241cbfc5769aa97e7f","tid":2259363,"uid":245849,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ebf4347de40bc5c9670d8f82de60f56550f496ee","tid":2259363,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5e88a9c135a987e9569870035cb03bd96639fe03","tid":2259363,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"aa9b2f5a9fa228596bb4aa24dcc12d5bd454ddf4","tid":2259363,"uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T19:16:06.000Z","msg":"612都俾好多法律以外既支援<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://612fund.hk/zh/latest-report\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F612fund.hk%2Fzh%2Flatest-report&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=bf2367b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://612fund.hk/zh/latest-report</a><br />\n<br />\n應唔應該打係case by case睇<br />\n依家任你講幾黑暗<br />\n都有巴打指出入罪率都係一半<br />\n仲未計有律師較易打甩較重罪名"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T19:29:17.000Z","msg":"成本效益太低。要建軍同維持，就要每個月燒幾千萬，startup就要幾億。當然你會話冇渠道，但我更擔心渠道出現之後已經冇錢，因為已經用晒。又或者經費不足，導致軍力不足。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T19:30:29.000Z","msg":"你收撚皮啦建軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講埋啲垃圾借口"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T20:00:33.000Z","msg":"中共有核彈，香港冇核彈，香港人一定要研究到核彈先有得打！"},{"pid":"17572b5a4e76e7eeef3204c17bc1fe24e3b0e86b","tid":2259363,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d591a4d8d8fd35322997a9241cbfc5769aa97e7f","tid":2259363,"uid":245849,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ebf4347de40bc5c9670d8f82de60f56550f496ee","tid":2259363,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5e88a9c135a987e9569870035cb03bd96639fe03","tid":2259363,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T19:29:17.000Z","msg":"成本效益太低。要建軍同維持，就要每個月燒幾千萬，startup就要幾億。當然你會話冇渠道，但我更擔心渠道出現之後已經冇錢，因為已經用晒。又或者經費不足，導致軍力不足。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T19:30:29.000Z","msg":"你收撚皮啦建軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講埋啲垃圾借口"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T20:00:33.000Z","msg":"中共有核彈，香港冇核彈，香港人一定要研究到核彈先有得打！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T20:03:07.000Z","msg":"我同你講有個612軍火基金<br />\n你覺得有冇人捐，你敢唔敢捐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face