259363,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2db56e97e558a4a2353d7e7a3bab683672e8b040","tid":2259363,"uid":245849,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"17572b5a4e76e7eeef3204c17bc1fe24e3b0e86b","tid":2259363,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d591a4d8d8fd35322997a9241cbfc5769aa97e7f","tid":2259363,"uid":245849,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T20:00:33.000Z","msg":"中共有核彈，香港冇核彈，香港人一定要研究到核彈先有得打！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T20:03:07.000Z","msg":"我同你講有個612軍火基金<br />\n你覺得有冇人捐，你敢唔敢捐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n捐612既95%係淺黃<br />\n唔捐612既錢係絕對唔流去&lsquo;革命&rsquo;<br />\n樓主既廢話只係叫人唔撚捐既借口"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T20:12:34.000Z","msg":"捐錢都唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果６１２捐錢資料會流出一樣好多人縮，唔關捐款性質問題；家陣你出錢，有人出命，香港人開心都嚟唔切，唔係之前點會成班人鬼叫請外國傭兵。屌，其實係香港人唔覺得香港人有得打，唔會請返香港人做兵先係最基本問題。<br />\n<br />\n俾槍俾子彈，有個巢穴，有情報系統，有戰略參謀部，最低工資，有冇人ＪＯＩＮ？我ＪＯＩＮ，完。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T20:18:41.000Z","msg":"現實就係同你講唔敢<br />\n資料流出係另一問題<br />\n612本身係合格組織做合法野<br />\n<br />\n你開個戶口話嚟做你話做既野，向人籌錢<br />\n我肯撚定淺黃唔會捐<br />\n同埋銀行會唔封你？<br />\n你覺得狗隊唔會做野？<br />\n<br />\n唔理唔識現實既執行困難<br />\n淨係識打飛機做革命義士<br />\n講嚟嘥氣"},{"pid":"693899167ca7ed12ba2f0b798477eb24e66df0be","tid":2259363,"uid":245849,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a24b245bbb72e5977515a744f5f9f716ed4ff74c","tid":2259363,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2db56e97e558a4a2353d7e7a3ba